<textBlocks>
	<container id="formVBox">
		<textBlock>
			<text
			size="25.0"
			fontFamily="System"
			fontStyle="Regular"
			text="Storytelling: Understanding community experiences with hazards, disasters, and threats">
			</text>
		</textBlock>
		<textBlock>
			<text
			size="16.0"
			fontFamily="System"
			fontStyle="Regular"
			text="In this activity you will engage members of the community in sharing stories about hazards and disasters they have experienced.">
			</text>
		</textBlock>
		<textBlock>
			<text
			size="16.0"
			fontFamily="System"
			fontStyle="Bold"
			text="Why do this: ">
			</text>
			<text
			size="16.0"
			fontFamily="System"
			fontStyle="Regular"
			text="Sharing stories provides an opportunity to understand community members concerns and perspectives based on real life experiences. The experiences shared provide a basis for discussion of equity issues and identifying actions. As a workshop activity, it helps people get to know each other better and create a collaborative atmosphere.">
			</text>
		</textBlock>
		<textBlock>
			<text
			size="16.0"
			fontFamily="System"
			fontStyle="Bold"
			text="How to do this: ">
			</text>
			<text
			size="16.0"
			fontFamily="System"
			fontStyle="Regular"
			text="&#xD;- Arrange participants into groups of 3.">
			</text>
			<text
			size="16.0"
			fontFamily="System"
			fontStyle="Regular"
			text="&#xD;- Hand out ">
			</text>
			<text
			size="16.0"
			fontFamily="System"
			fontStyle="Hyperlink"
			text="hazards storytelling worksheets"
			linkType="externalDOC"
			link="Ch3_hazards_storytelling_worksheets.docx">
			</text>
			<text
			size="16.0"
			fontFamily="System"
			fontStyle="Regular"
			text="&#xD;&#x9;- Facilitators should role play storytelling activity instructions">
			</text>
			<text
			size="16.0"
			fontFamily="System"
			fontStyle="Regular"
			text="&#xD;&#x9;&#x9;- Participants will have 3 minutes to think about the story prompt and jot down some notes on their worksheet.">
			</text>
			<text
			size="16.0"
			fontFamily="System"
			fontStyle="Regular"
			text="&#xD;&#x9;&#x9;- One participant will have 7 minutes to share their story with the others in their group.">
			</text>
			<text
			size="16.0"
			fontFamily="System"
			fontStyle="Regular"
			text="&#xD;&#x9;&#x9;- After 7 minutes the facilitator will call for everyone to switch roles, until everyone has had a chance to tell their story.">
			</text>
			<text
			size="16.0"
			fontFamily="System"
			fontStyle="Regular"
			text="&#xD;&#x9;&#x9;- After everyone has shared a story, get back together in the larger group and discuss key themes from the stories.">
			</text>
			<text
			size="16.0"
			fontFamily="System"
			fontStyle="Regular"
			text="&#xD;&#x9;- Add notes to the ">
			</text>
			<text
			size="16.0"
			fontFamily="System"
			fontStyle="Hyperlink"
			text=" Chapter 3 summary form"
			linkType="internalStep"
			link="301">
			</text>
		</textBlock>
	</container>
